junit.framework.Test
public class XPathPosIndexTest
extends AbstractQueryTest

Tests if the repository supports position index in XPath. The tests will check the repository descriptor Repository.QUERY_XPATH_POS_INDEX first and throw a NotExecutableException if the descriptor is not present.

This is a level 1 test, therefore does not write content to the workspace. The tests require the following content in the default workspace:

At least three nodes with the name AbstractJCRTest.nodeName1 under the AbstractJCRTest.testRoot.
